Class PlayerAttackEntityEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.event.Event
      • net.yatopia.api.event.PlayerAttackEntityEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cancellable

    public class PlayerAttackEntityEvent
extends Event
implements Cancellable
    Called when the Player attacks a Entity.

    This event is fired earlier than EntityDamageByEntityEvent .
